results.name: a(n) = Sum_{d|n} phi(d^3).
link: Harvey P. Dale, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
formula: Also Sum_{d|n} d*phi(d^2), or Sum_{d|n} d^2*phi(d).
Also Sum_{k=1..n} (n/gcd(n, k))^2 = Sum_{k=1..n} (lcm(n, k)/k)^2. - _Vladeta Jovovic_, Dec 29 2002
G.f.: Sum_{k>=1} k^2*phi(k)*x^k/(1 - x^k). - _Ilya Gutkovskiy_, Mar 10 2018
Dirichlet g.f.: Sum_{n>=1} a(n) / n^s = zeta(s) * zeta(s-3) / zeta(s-2). - _Werner Schulte_, Feb 18 2021
program: (PARI) a(n) = sumdiv(n, d, eulerphi(d^3)); \\ _Michel Marcus_, Mar 10 2018
results.author: _Benoit Cloitre_, Apr 06 2002
